{"tid":2314093,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"整爛道具丨「哈利仔」丹尼爾大爆拍攝趣聞 經常弄斷魔仗全因衰貪玩","createTime":"2020-12-06T09:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T10:55:28.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"26560744d74d5d44c15929b2219eaf8d6c31842e","tid":2314093,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T09:48:41.000Z","msg":"《哈利波特》的魔法世界中，人人都會手執一支魔仗施法，但丹尼爾就表示自己弄斷了多支魔仗：「我弄斷很多魔仗，因為我喜歡在腳上扮打鼓，因此每隔3、4個星期，魔仗就會斷，所以我就會對道具大哥感到很抱歉，他就會給予我『不要再打鼓』的表情。」另外，他又回應外間說他打破了過百副眼鏡的傳聞：「報道誇張了，我一定不是經常打爛眼鏡。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201206/FNWSTFT3ZZD3FA7MFN276WQKL4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201206%2FFNWSTFT3ZZD3FA7MFN276WQKL4%2F&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2puyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=a8d9baa2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201206%2FFNWSTFT3ZZD3FA7MFN276WQKL4%2F&h=b52689f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201206/FNWSTFT3ZZD3FA7MFN276WQKL4/</a>"},{"pid":"207bdf0296ce439fde6a7a7a9c9f4c80a926fd0f","tid":2314093,"uid":24457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T17:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/d6/1e/e3/d61ee379ade3f656940d5fed2dedb923.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fd6%2F1e%2Fe3%2Fd61ee379ade3f656940d5fed2dedb923.jpg&h=9856b773&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同馬份玩得多緊係斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8267d0b7943553b77e0c018603d98158d46b3b50","tid":2314093,"uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"207bdf0296ce439fde6a7a7a9c9f4c80a926fd0f","tid":2314093,"uid":24457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T17:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/d6/1e/e3/d61ee379ade3f656940d5fed2dedb923.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/